- Eun Byul...

125
00:11:00,379 --> 00:11:01,549
Eun Byul je v nebezpečí.

126
00:11:01,549 --> 00:11:03,519
Najdeme ji.

127
00:11:03,519 --> 00:11:05,649
Hwang Kyung Il řekl,

128
00:11:06,249 --> 00:11:08,119
